INSERT INTO `aq_post` VALUES ('7', 'Ugrid无人机智能操作系统（UOS）', '3', '1529655120', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ugrid无人机智能操作系统是基于大疆SDK针对电力巡航作业特点深度定制的无人机操作系统，使电网巡视作业安全可靠。该系统能全自动完成输变配线路的精细化巡视（配合RTK使用）、通道巡视、灾情评估、资产全景等外业数据采集工作。</p><p><img src=\"http://yanshi.sucaihuo.com/modals/40/4002/demo/images/products/pro6-1.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">无人机智能操作系统是基于大疆SDK开发的、针对电力巡航作业特点深度定制的无人机操作系统。系统涵盖了电网的精细化巡检和通道巡检，通过无人机的智能控制，能够清楚、准确发现电网周围环境和本地的潜在危险和缺陷。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">杆塔精细化巡检模块上的学习模式可以按照不同塔型记录和存储无人机的飞行轨迹和拍摄位置。所记录的飞行信息将作为下次飞行依据在自动化巡检模式中使用，实现无人机的自动精细化巡检，降低对巡视人员的无人机操控素质的要求，大大降低了巡视成本，提升了杆塔巡检的效率，保证了电网巡视作业的安全。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; ma